1
00:00:30,950 --> 00:00:33,270
[You Have My Heart]

2
00:00:33,290 --> 00:00:36,270
[Episode 9: Truth as Bait]

3
00:00:45,500 --> 00:00:47,360
The pool water has dropped again.

4
00:00:47,470 --> 00:00:48,680
The spiritual power isn't increasing,

5
00:00:48,680 --> 00:00:50,640
but the evil power is
popping up everywhere.

6
00:00:50,640 --> 00:00:51,880
If this continues,

7
00:00:52,110 --> 00:00:54,710
I'm afraid we won't
survive this rainy season.

8
00:00:54,880 --> 00:00:56,280
I was on duty yesterday.

9
00:00:56,670 --> 00:00:58,640
When I got close to the evil power rift,

10
00:00:58,640 --> 00:00:59,560
the force was

11
00:00:59,920 --> 00:01:01,840
ten times fiercer than usual.

12
00:01:05,000 --> 00:01:06,000
Freshly tainted?

13
00:01:06,510 --> 00:01:07,760
While washing clothes,

14
00:01:07,760 --> 00:01:09,760
I accidentally got it on my forearm.

15
00:01:10,680 --> 00:01:12,680
I hope Lady Fufeng can hold on.

16
00:01:12,950 --> 00:01:14,400
If even she...

17
00:01:17,039 --> 00:01:17,640
Master.

18
00:01:17,840 --> 00:01:18,840
That Young Magistrate

19
00:01:18,840 --> 00:01:20,480
took the selected scrolls early
this morning

20
00:01:20,480 --> 00:01:22,840
and went down the mountain
back to the county yamen.

21
00:01:22,840 --> 00:01:23,710
I see.

22
00:01:24,200 --> 00:01:25,840
He put on a good act,

23
00:01:26,070 --> 00:01:27,530
but he left just like that.

24
00:01:28,560 --> 00:01:30,490
I didn't expect him to do anything.

25
00:01:33,640 --> 00:01:37,259
That day, I noticed that the evil power
in Kuquan Valley was restless.

26
00:01:37,259 --> 00:01:39,190
I'm afraid something will happen.

27
00:01:39,840 --> 00:01:41,759
Lead all the spirit envoys

28
00:01:42,039 --> 00:01:43,940
and the spirits of Xiqianhua
to suppress it.

29
00:01:43,940 --> 00:01:45,200
You must hold the line.

30
00:01:46,640 --> 00:01:49,870
Then, are you going to be alright

31
00:01:50,430 --> 00:01:51,360
if you are alone?

32
00:01:52,350 --> 00:01:53,000
It's okay.

33
00:01:53,920 --> 00:01:54,789
Go ahead.

34
00:01:55,560 --> 00:01:56,150
Yes.

35
00:02:24,000 --> 00:02:25,000
Clumsy.

36
00:02:28,910 --> 00:02:29,910
Am I not handsome?

37
00:02:33,710 --> 00:02:34,840
I'm sorry, Lord Bai.

38
00:02:35,670 --> 00:02:37,079
I was reckless.

39
00:02:39,190 --> 00:02:40,840
Sorry, I was just upset.

40
00:02:45,800 --> 00:02:47,560
Is something bothering you?

41
00:02:47,910 --> 00:02:48,800
Nothing.

42
00:02:52,710 --> 00:02:53,370
Let me do it.

43
00:02:56,910 --> 00:02:58,640
If you are worried about cases,

44
00:02:58,710 --> 00:02:59,520
you can ask me.

45
00:03:00,000 --> 00:03:01,520
I know everything,

46
00:03:01,960 --> 00:03:03,080
from humans to demons,

47
00:03:03,080 --> 00:03:04,340
in Yin-Yang Crossing.

48
00:03:04,800 --> 00:03:05,360
Really?

49
00:03:05,590 --> 00:03:06,190
Of course.

50
00:03:06,360 --> 00:03:09,080
Then, if demons get hurt,
how should they get treated?

51
00:03:09,080 --> 00:03:10,430
If they get hurt,

52
00:03:10,560 --> 00:03:12,760
they must be treated with demonic arts.

53
00:03:13,510 --> 00:03:14,800
It also depends on the situation.

54
00:03:14,800 --> 00:03:16,150
Whether it's an injury

55
00:03:16,150 --> 00:03:18,190
or they got possessed during cultivation.

56
00:03:18,190 --> 00:03:20,630
Your question is too amateur.

57
00:03:21,560 --> 00:03:23,829
What if their spiritual power is damaged?

58
00:03:23,829 --> 00:03:25,470
What medicine should be used?

59
00:03:25,470 --> 00:03:26,120
Medicine?

60
00:03:27,560 --> 00:03:30,560
There should be
spiritual power replenishment.

61
00:03:32,470 --> 00:03:34,400
Treating like with like, you know.

62
00:03:34,800 --> 00:03:36,329
The medicine we humans take

63
00:03:36,430 --> 00:03:37,870
is useless for demons.

64
00:03:38,630 --> 00:03:40,470
But I read in the ancient records

65
00:03:40,800 --> 00:03:43,200
that some medicines are useful for demons.

66
00:03:44,240 --> 00:03:46,030
Could it be a deceptive book?

67
00:03:51,190 --> 00:03:52,430
You haven't read any books anyway.

68
00:03:52,430 --> 00:03:53,690
Asking you is useless.

69
00:03:54,920 --> 00:03:56,440
What do you mean?

70
00:03:57,190 --> 00:03:57,870
Besides,

71
00:03:58,360 --> 00:03:59,560
look at my movements.

72
00:03:59,910 --> 00:04:01,440
It's obvious I'm a warrior.

73
00:04:15,560 --> 00:04:16,630
What are you doing?

74
00:04:17,870 --> 00:04:18,930
Brewing medicine.

75
00:04:38,270 --> 00:04:40,130
Do you think the medicine you brew

76
00:04:40,840 --> 00:04:42,080
can cure demons?

77
00:04:43,950 --> 00:04:45,800
I went to your secret room

78
00:04:45,940 --> 00:04:47,680
and found some records related to demons.

79
00:04:47,680 --> 00:04:49,190
I found some spiritual medicines

80
00:04:49,190 --> 00:04:51,050
that have miraculous effects on
restoring spiritual power.

81
00:04:51,050 --> 00:04:52,800
So, I brewed some to try.

82
00:04:55,040 --> 00:04:56,840
You have a lot of spare time, huh?

83
00:04:58,900 --> 00:04:59,950
Don't worry, My Lady.

84
00:04:59,950 --> 00:05:01,560
I didn't delay any official business.

85
00:05:01,560 --> 00:05:04,560
There are just
a few disputes among spirits

86
00:05:04,650 --> 00:05:05,920
that I'm not sure about.

87
00:05:05,920 --> 00:05:08,310
I'll wait until you recover
to make a decision.

88
00:05:08,310 --> 00:05:10,800
So, please take your medicine.

89
00:05:11,160 --> 00:05:14,020
You can't abandon
the people of Yin-Yang Crossing.

90
00:05:15,750 --> 00:05:16,600
Take a look.

91
00:05:30,920 --> 00:05:32,320
Don't waste your effort.

92
00:05:32,720 --> 00:05:34,380
Even if you brew ten more pots,

93
00:05:34,630 --> 00:05:36,290
it's just a drop in the bucket.

94
00:05:36,640 --> 00:05:38,230
It smells bad,

95
00:05:38,510 --> 00:05:39,800
but it's effective.

96
00:05:40,450 --> 00:05:42,180
You'd better drink it, My Lady.

97
00:05:45,560 --> 00:05:48,270
I'm a mortal with a lifespan of
several decades.

98
00:05:48,780 --> 00:05:50,780
I'm only working here temporarily.

99
00:05:50,870 --> 00:05:52,480
I don't know what arrangements

100
00:05:52,480 --> 00:05:53,870
the court will have for me later.

101
00:05:53,870 --> 00:05:54,750
So, My Lady,

102
00:05:54,950 --> 00:05:57,040
you can't pin your hopes on me.

103
00:05:57,390 --> 00:05:59,800
Since you have guarded Yin-Yang Crossing
for thousands of years,

104
00:05:59,800 --> 00:06:01,460
you must continue to guard it.

105
00:06:04,870 --> 00:06:05,830
Bai Shanjun.

106
00:06:07,720 --> 00:06:09,450
Are you really willing to stay?

107
00:06:11,290 --> 00:06:12,600
I decocted medicine and served you

108
00:06:12,600 --> 00:06:14,040
willingly.

109
00:06:14,720 --> 00:06:17,040
Please don't give up.

110
00:06:54,070 --> 00:06:54,530
My Lady.

111
00:06:55,240 --> 00:06:56,970
This is another prescription.

112
00:06:59,950 --> 00:07:00,800
Taste it.

113
00:07:11,370 --> 00:07:12,370
It's very bitter.

114
00:07:13,030 --> 00:07:14,960
Why didn't you put some honey in it?

115
00:07:15,560 --> 00:07:16,120
I will.

116
00:07:30,870 --> 00:07:31,330
My Lady.

117
00:07:32,190 --> 00:07:33,240
The light is so dim

118
00:07:33,750 --> 00:07:34,750
that it upsets me.

119
00:07:36,120 --> 00:07:37,780
Bring that candlestick over.

120
00:07:37,920 --> 00:07:38,390
Okay.

121
00:07:46,430 --> 00:07:47,430
My legs are sore.

122
00:07:47,750 --> 00:07:48,510
Lord Bai,

123
00:07:49,070 --> 00:07:50,730
could you massage them for me?

124
00:07:50,830 --> 00:07:51,480
Okay.

125
00:07:57,700 --> 00:07:58,159
My Lady,

126
00:07:58,330 --> 00:08:00,730
it is inappropriate for a man
to touch a woman.

127
00:08:00,730 --> 00:08:02,120
I will find a wooden mallet tomorrow

128
00:08:02,120 --> 00:08:03,360
to massage your legs.

129
00:08:04,390 --> 00:08:05,270
Bai Shanjun,

130
00:08:06,360 --> 00:08:08,020
you seem to care about me a lot.

131
00:08:12,510 --> 00:08:12,970
My Lady,

132
00:08:13,630 --> 00:08:15,090
everyone cares about you.

133
00:08:17,630 --> 00:08:19,030
When you first came here,

134
00:08:19,630 --> 00:08:20,750
you looked gentle,

135
00:08:21,360 --> 00:08:23,420
but you were actually very stubborn.

136
00:08:23,800 --> 00:08:24,920
Now it seems

137
00:08:25,870 --> 00:08:27,560
you have became gentler.

138
00:08:28,680 --> 00:08:29,270
My Lady,

139
00:08:29,650 --> 00:08:30,930
when we first met,

140
00:08:31,020 --> 00:08:32,250
you wanted to kill me.

141
00:08:32,480 --> 00:08:33,909
If I weren't tough enough,

142
00:08:33,909 --> 00:08:35,710
I would probably be ashes by now.

143
00:08:43,150 --> 00:08:43,630
My Lady.

144
00:08:54,320 --> 00:08:55,320
Bai Shanjun,

145
00:08:57,120 --> 00:08:58,030
what if...

146
00:08:58,150 --> 00:08:58,440
My Lady,

147
00:08:58,440 --> 00:08:58,720
I...

148
00:08:59,300 --> 00:09:00,480
There are no what-ifs.

149
00:09:00,480 --> 00:09:02,280
You will definitely get better.

150
00:09:42,720 --> 00:09:43,270
My Lady.

151
00:09:45,550 --> 00:09:46,120
My Lady?

152
00:10:56,320 --> 00:10:58,170
[May Lady Fufeng recover.
From Bai Shanjun.]

153
00:10:59,550 --> 00:11:00,120
My Lady.

154
00:11:01,690 --> 00:11:03,020
I pray to you,

155
00:11:03,670 --> 00:11:05,330
wishing for your good health.

156
00:11:05,910 --> 00:11:07,360
Is it strange?

157
00:11:10,300 --> 00:11:11,780
But don't you fulfill

158
00:11:12,270 --> 00:11:13,870
all the wishes of the people?

159
00:11:15,270 --> 00:11:16,270
I, Bai Shanjun,

160
00:11:17,170 --> 00:11:18,740
am also one of your people.

161
00:11:19,930 --> 00:11:20,720
My Lady,

162
00:11:22,030 --> 00:11:23,720
can you fulfill my wish?

163
00:11:37,960 --> 00:11:38,840
Who is there?

164
00:11:54,510 --> 00:11:55,230
Who are you?

165
00:11:56,960 --> 00:11:57,720
Me?

166
00:11:58,640 --> 00:11:59,760
I am you.

167
00:12:02,480 --> 00:12:03,480
Have you been

168
00:12:03,590 --> 00:12:04,950
looking for this?

169
00:12:08,150 --> 00:12:09,390
Look closely.

170
00:12:09,630 --> 00:12:11,160
Is this the answer you want?

171
00:12:11,960 --> 00:12:13,160
Stop playing tricks!

172
00:12:13,720 --> 00:12:15,630
How could there be two of me
in this world?

173
00:12:15,630 --> 00:12:16,720
Who exactly are you?

174
00:12:16,720 --> 00:12:17,650
What do you want?

175
00:12:17,990 --> 00:12:19,110
How stubborn.

176
00:12:20,910 --> 00:12:23,150
I have been patient enough with you,

177
00:12:23,510 --> 00:12:25,750
but you ruined my plans time and again.

178
00:13:07,600 --> 00:13:09,060
It's been a hundred years,

179
00:13:09,360 --> 00:13:12,490
and you still only use
these sneaky, despicable tricks,

180
00:13:12,910 --> 00:13:13,720
Bai Han.

181
00:13:21,410 --> 00:13:23,070
You were faking your illness.

182
00:13:23,360 --> 00:13:24,910
Realizing it now

183
00:13:25,890 --> 00:13:27,090
is probably too late.

184
00:13:27,440 --> 00:13:29,440
Lead all the spirit envoys

185
00:13:29,750 --> 00:13:31,730
and the spirits of Xiqianhua
to suppress it.

186
00:13:31,730 --> 00:13:32,990
You must hold the line.

187
00:13:34,510 --> 00:13:37,750
Then, is it okay for you

188
00:13:38,310 --> 00:13:39,190
to be alone?

189
00:13:40,270 --> 00:13:41,030
It's okay.

190
00:13:41,840 --> 00:13:42,720
Go ahead.

191
00:14:01,390 --> 00:14:02,600
You little spirit.

192
00:14:03,520 --> 00:14:04,790
You are still alive?

193
00:14:05,270 --> 00:14:06,670
Lady Fufeng anticipated

194
00:14:06,960 --> 00:14:08,720
that you would kill me after using me,

195
00:14:08,720 --> 00:14:10,690
so she made a substitute
with her spiritual power

196
00:14:10,690 --> 00:14:12,350
to lure you into devouring it.

197
00:14:12,480 --> 00:14:13,480
What you devoured

198
00:14:13,790 --> 00:14:16,240
was just a bait made of
My Lady's pure spiritual power.

199
00:14:16,240 --> 00:14:16,870
Bai Han,

200
00:14:17,270 --> 00:14:18,030
stop it.

201
00:14:18,750 --> 00:14:19,910
Fine.

202
00:14:45,510 --> 00:14:46,570
My Lord and My Lady.

203
00:14:48,630 --> 00:14:49,750
I have paid for

204
00:14:51,790 --> 00:14:52,720
what I owed you.

205
00:15:09,510 --> 00:15:10,480
She has always felt guilty

206
00:15:10,480 --> 00:15:12,390
for almost hurting you that day.

207
00:15:12,870 --> 00:15:15,000
Just consider it her compensation.

208
00:15:15,220 --> 00:15:17,950
But there was no need to
compensate with her life.

209
00:15:18,840 --> 00:15:21,300
Though the mirror is broken,
it can be fixed.

210
00:15:22,030 --> 00:15:23,360
Can she come back?

211
00:15:33,270 --> 00:15:35,470
Don't be afraid, little bronze mirror.

212
00:15:36,480 --> 00:15:37,600
This place

213
00:15:38,240 --> 00:15:39,770
is full of spiritual power.

214
00:15:43,150 --> 00:15:44,670
In less than a hundred years,

215
00:15:44,670 --> 00:15:46,870
you'll be able to take human form again.

216
00:15:59,600 --> 00:16:00,150
My Lady,

217
00:16:02,630 --> 00:16:04,780
the one who stole your heart
a hundred years ago

218
00:16:04,780 --> 00:16:05,840
was Bai Han, right?

219
00:16:13,150 --> 00:16:14,360
Did you get it back?

220
00:16:26,070 --> 00:16:26,950
Will you die?

221
00:16:35,480 --> 00:16:37,610
There's no point discussing this now.

222
00:16:40,910 --> 00:16:42,170
Bai Han is still alive,

223
00:16:42,200 --> 00:16:44,460
hiding somewhere in Yin-Yang Crossing.

224
00:16:44,550 --> 00:16:45,860
I must lure him out to

225
00:16:46,390 --> 00:16:48,150
eliminate the root of the problem.

226
00:16:48,150 --> 00:16:48,960
So,

227
00:16:50,580 --> 00:16:53,180
your injury and being bedridden
were all fake.

228
00:16:55,270 --> 00:16:55,670
Yes.

229
00:16:57,150 --> 00:16:58,720
Why didn't you tell me?

230
00:16:59,360 --> 00:17:00,270
Bai Shanjun,

231
00:17:00,840 --> 00:17:02,150
if I told you everything,

232
00:17:02,150 --> 00:17:03,750
other than making you worry,

233
00:17:04,030 --> 00:17:05,359
what would be the point?

234
00:17:07,680 --> 00:17:08,240
Fine.

235
00:17:09,440 --> 00:17:10,829
Since you're fine, My Lady,

236
00:17:10,829 --> 00:17:13,680
I won't disturb you anymore.

237
00:17:25,680 --> 00:17:26,270
My Lady,

238
00:17:28,030 --> 00:17:29,750
I'm angry that you deceived me,

239
00:17:29,750 --> 00:17:31,680
watching me run around like a fool.

240
00:17:31,890 --> 00:17:32,540
I know

241
00:17:32,920 --> 00:17:34,920
little about Yin-Yang Crossing
and evil power,

242
00:17:34,920 --> 00:17:36,960
so I understand why
you didn't tell me the truth.

243
00:17:36,960 --> 00:17:38,590
But I never wanted you to die.

244
00:17:45,310 --> 00:17:46,110
It's good

245
00:17:47,160 --> 00:17:48,160
that you're fine.

246
00:17:59,510 --> 00:18:01,160
Though you're not a fool,

247
00:18:01,880 --> 00:18:03,070
you're a nerd.

248
00:18:04,200 --> 00:18:06,550
Why did Bai Han choose you

249
00:18:07,160 --> 00:18:08,270
to be his vessel?

250
00:18:11,590 --> 00:18:12,200
Master,

251
00:18:12,790 --> 00:18:13,790
has the evil power

252
00:18:14,030 --> 00:18:15,200
dissipated?

253
00:18:16,350 --> 00:18:17,350
I felt that

254
00:18:17,960 --> 00:18:19,750
it went a bit too smoothly.

255
00:18:20,750 --> 00:18:21,640
Smoothly?

256
00:18:23,030 --> 00:18:24,750
If the evil power is
dispersed in one place,

257
00:18:24,750 --> 00:18:26,550
it will return from another.

258
00:18:26,880 --> 00:18:28,510
In the past hundred years, Bai Han

259
00:18:28,510 --> 00:18:30,710
must have learned many wicked methods.

260
00:18:31,440 --> 00:18:33,640
He's harder to deal with than I thought.

261
00:18:33,680 --> 00:18:34,270
Then,

262
00:18:35,400 --> 00:18:37,750
can we take back

263
00:18:38,270 --> 00:18:40,670
the half tree heart
in Bai Shanjun's chest?

264
00:18:42,200 --> 00:18:43,730
It's not the right time yet.

265
00:18:59,960 --> 00:19:01,820
Send someone to the capital to ask

266
00:19:02,160 --> 00:19:03,310
if the person in the painting

267
00:19:03,310 --> 00:19:04,200
is really

268
00:19:04,200 --> 00:19:07,480
the county magistrate demoted
from the capital to Yin-Yang Crossing,

269
00:19:07,480 --> 00:19:08,550
Bai Shanjun.

270
00:19:10,550 --> 00:19:10,960
Yes.

271
00:19:22,090 --> 00:19:26,680
[May Lady Fufeng recover.
From Bai Shanjun.]

272
00:19:32,440 --> 00:19:33,440
Thank you.

